## Design System

**Palette (locked — Q1 research confirmed antique gold as the elite boutique law signal):**
- Background: `#0D0D0D` (near-black; less harsh than pure black)
- Surface: `#141414`
- Text primary: `#F5F3EF` (warm white)
- Text secondary: `#9E9E9E`
- Accent: `#C9A96E` (antique gold — full opacity for CTAs + ruled lines only)
- Accent hover: `#B8955A`
- Accent decorative: `#C9A96E` at 40% opacity (dividers)
- Danger: `#C0392B`

**Typography:**
- Headline: `Cormorant Garamond` 300/400 (Google Fonts) — Didone/transitional, editorial weight
- Subhead: `Cormorant Garamond` 600 italic
- Body: `Inter` 400/400
- Caption/meta: `Inter` 300, letter-spacing +0.08em, small-caps where possible
- Mono (AI output stream): `JetBrains Mono` (already in portfolio; acceptable for CMS internal UI only, not public site)

**Motion vocabulary:**
- Page entry: 500ms `opacity 0→1` + `translateY(16px→0)`, `ease-out`, staggered by 80ms
- Hero parallax: `background-position` slow-scroll (CSS scroll-driven or JS rAF)
- Navigation hover: 200ms bottom-border slide from left (CSS transform)
- CMS panel transitions: 300ms `translateX` slide-in
- No spring, no bounce — editorial stillness throughout

**Layout conventions:**
- Max content width: 1280px centered
- Grid: 12-col; editorial pages use asymmetric (2+8+2 or 1+6+1+4 for sidebar)
- Ruled lines: `1px solid #D0CBBE` horizontal dividers, generous padding above/below
- Large captioned imagery: full-bleed hero (100vh), 16:9 practice-area hero band
- CMS admin: clean white cards, no editorial drama — utility-focused

**Confirmed nav structure (Gibson Dunn / Quinn Emanuel reference — Q5):**
```
[Logo]  Practice Areas | Publications | About | Contact  [EN/ES/FR]  [Contact CTA button]
```
Desktop: horizontal, smallcaps labels, no mega-menus. Mobile: hamburger → full-screen overlay with locale switcher.

**Confirmed hero pattern (Q5):** Full-viewport B&W editorial image, 60–80px Cormorant Garamond serif headline, subhead 18px Inter, single gold CTA button. Optional slow looping B&W video at low opacity.

**Confirmed publications layout (Q5):** 3-column card grid. Each card: gold category tag, Cormorant headline, date, excerpt, "Read more" link. Filter bar: All | Client Alerts | Articles | Firm News.

**Confirmed practice-area page layout (Q5):** Full-width header + gold accent rule, sticky left nav (sub-practices), main content: rich prose + related publications feed.

**Tailwind config (`tailwind.config.js`) — custom tokens:**
```js
theme.extend.colors: {
  'bg-base': '#0D0D0D', 'bg-surface': '#141414',
  'text-primary': '#F5F3EF', 'text-secondary': '#9E9E9E',
  'accent': '#C9A96E', 'accent-hover': '#B8955A', 'rule': '#D0CBBE'
}
theme.extend.fontFamily: { serif: ['Cormorant Garamond', 'Georgia', 'serif'], sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'] }
```

