1. `mw-backend/solo_law_blueprint.py` — entire Flask OOP backend
2. `src/app/app.module.ts` + `app-routing.module.ts` — Angular module + routes
3. `src/app/services/api.service.ts` — HTTP + auth headers
4. `src/app/services/ai-agent.service.ts` — WebLLM agentic controller
5. `src/app/services/i18n.service.ts` — locale management
6. `src/app/pages/home/home.component.{ts,html,css}` — hero + PA preview + publications preview
7. `src/app/pages/practice-areas/` — list + detail components
8. `src/app/pages/publications/` — list + detail components
9. `src/app/pages/cms/` — CMS shell, login, dashboard, PA editor, pub editor, asset library
10. `src/app/components/shared/` — locale-switcher, nav, footer, ai-assist-panel
11. `src/styles.css` — Tailwind directives + global editorial CSS
12. `tailwind.config.js` — custom design tokens

