| Q4 Playwright | `--headless=new --use-angle=vulkan --enable-features=Vulkan,WebGPU --disable-vulkan-surface --enable-unsafe-webgpu --ignore-gpu-blocklist`; CI without GPU hits mock fallback automatically |
